title: Free Agent RB Rankings, Cowboys offer Dak, Hollywood Tom Brady? (Football 3/10)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to start Free Agency Preview Week. First, the guys discuss a reported new offer for Dak Prescott and try to understand why the Cowboys won't just pay up already (3:20). Next, Tom Brady is headed to Hollywood (18:00)! Well, at least his new production company is...What does this mean for his free agency though? The Pick Six Superfriends hit on some movement among former secondary studs, Josh Norman and Trumaine Johnson (30:15). They also comment on the Rams new logo (39:15) and Austin Ekeler's new deal (41:45), before ranking this year's free agent running back class and assigning ideal landing spots for the Top 5 (45:00).

'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
